{
  "texts": [
    "Their results (passed or failed) are compared.",
    "The TUE is marked as success for that DUT if the results of the TUE and GTB match.",
    "The proportion of successes is the ratio of matches between the TUE and GTB with respect to all the DUT mutants, which represents the coverage of the TUE.",
    "A testbench passes Eval2 if the Eval2 ratio exceeds a threshold 𝑅, set to 80% in Section 5.The mutants of the golden RTL codes are generated by the LLM.",
    "The LLM is provided with the golden RTL code and asked to generate 𝑁 𝑚 mutants by making minor modifications evenly on the code."
  ]
}